# Campaign 

## Go Logic
1. Handlers
    a. leadPageHandler - (/)
    b. SuccessHandler  - (/sucess.html)
    c. ErrorHanlder    - (/error.html)
2. URL - localhost:8080
3. DB - postgresql
4. LeadJSON
5. UnitTests

Version - 1 
## Application Flow
1. Take the Lead details from Lead Page
2. Store the Lead Details in Database.
3. Redirect to Success Page if the status is successfull.
4. Redirect to error Page if the status is failed.

## HTML Pages
1. LeadPage (Start Page)
2. Success Page
3. Error Page.

## Database
1. Campaign 
2. Leads 

## HTML Form Fields 
a. Salutation
b. FirstName
c. LastName
d. EMail Address.
e. Submit Button


